# Client Delivery — Backend Cleanup Walkthrough

## What Was Fixed

### 🔒 Security
- **API route protection via middleware** — `/api/admin/*`, `/api/student/*`, `/api/teacher/*` now reject unauthenticated or wrong-role requests at the edge (before hitting any handler)

### 🔴 Critical Data Flow Fixes
- **Student fees** — was reading from [FeeRecord](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/app/%28admin%29/admin/students/page.tsx#28-37) (wrong collection), now reads [StudentFee](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/StudentFee.ts#11-31) (same collection admin writes to)
- **Auto fee creation** — was using orphaned [CoursePricing](file:///media/swastik/focus/ldm%20feb/src/models/CoursePricing.ts#3-15) model, now reads `Program.pricing`
- **Course pricing sync** — was failing due to case mismatch (`dccm` vs `DCCM`), fixed with `trim().toLowerCase()` — synced 21/22 courses

### 🆕 New Student Features
- `GET /api/student/attendance` — detailed subject-wise attendance records
- `GET /api/student/notices` — active notices with expiry filtering
- `/student/attendance` page — summary cards, clickable status filters, detailed table with low-attendance warning
- Attendance link added to student dashboard

